Summary: Describes the themeable properties for the EditorSpinSlider, specifically the textures for its up/down buttons.
Theme Property: updown (Texture2D)
Single texture representing both the up and down buttons.
Theme Property: updown_disabled (Texture2D)
Single texture representing both the up and down buttons, when the control is readonly or disabled.